AddressInfo.Title: Rocky Mount Supercharger
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Located in the DoubleTree Rocky Mount parking lot.   From I-95 North:  Take exit 138-Tarboro to merge onto US-64 E,  Take exit 466 for Winstead Ave,  Turn right onto N Winstead Ave,  Take the 1st left onto Curtis Ellis Dr,  Take the 1st left onto Gateway Blvd,  Turn left into DoubleTree Rocky Mount.  /  From I-95 South:  Take exit 138 for US-64 E toward Rocky Mt,  Continue on the ramp and merge onto US-64 E,  Take exit 466 for Winstead Ave,  Turn right onto N Winstead Ave,  Take the 1st left onto Curtis Ellis Dr,  Take the 1st left onto Gateway Blvd,  Turn left into DoubleTree Rocky Mount.  /  From US-64 West:  Take exit 466 for Winstead Ave,  Turn right onto N Winstead Ave,  Take the 2nd left onto Curtis Ellis Dr,  Take the 1st left onto Gateway Blvd,  Turn left into DoubleTree Rocky Mount.  /  US-64 East:  Take exit 466 for Winstead Ave,  Turn right onto N Winstead Ave,  Take the 1st left onto Curtis Ellis Dr,  Take the 1st left onto Gateway Blvd,  Turn left into DoubleTree Rocky Mount.
